'''热带风暴芭芭拉'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Barbara}}）是[[2007年太平洋飓风季|2007年太平洋飓风季]]第一个[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]过的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统源于[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]东南方向约380公里海域的小规模[[低气压|低气压区]]，是本季形成的第2场风暴。系统起初向南飘移，之后转向稳步东进，强度很快就达到热带风暴标准。受[[风切变|风切变]]增多的影响，芭芭拉逐渐减弱，但很快又得以重新组织，在从墨西哥和[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]边界以西不远处登陆前不久达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度。进入陆地上空后，气旋迅速减弱，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于6月2日中止针对风暴发布公告。

气象机构起初预计芭芭拉会达到飓风标准，但气旋直到上岸时强度仍然不高，规模也较小。系统在局部地区产生暴雨和阵风，大部分地点所受破坏程度很轻。不过，墨西哥南部有大面积农田被暴雨摧毁，农作物损失总额达2亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（2007年墨西哥比索，相当于同年的5500万美元）。此外，萨尔瓦多还有4人因风暴引发的洪灾丧生。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Barbara 2007 track.png}}
热带风暴芭芭拉的源头估计是5月14日离开非洲海岸的一股[[东风波|东风波]]。系统向西移动，于5月25日穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]，次日进入东北[[太平洋|太平洋]]。东风波同[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]相互影响，所在海域于5月27日发展出大范围地面[[低气压|低气压区]]，系统向北飘移，在此期间组织结构趋于混乱，[[对流|对流]]也相对有限。5月29日，系统中的对流已有所增长，逐渐在低气压中心聚拢，<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Richard Knabb | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-01 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002014302/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP022007_Barbara.pdf | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP022007_Barbara.pdf | deadurl = no | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>东部半圆内还发展出[[雨带|带状特征]]，环流结束有显著改善<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.001.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | date =  }}</ref>。估计系统是于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月29日下午18点在[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]][[埃斯孔迪多港_(瓦哈卡州)|埃斯孔迪多港]]东南方向约185公里洋面发展成第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。成为热带气旋后，系统所在海域的[[海面温度|海面温度]]较高，[[风切变|风切变]]非常少，上层大气环境也有利于发展<ref name="disc1" />。

成为热带气旋之后的几小时里，系统中的深层对流出现衰减<ref name="disc2">{{cite report | author = Knabb | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Two | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-03-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.002.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | date =  }}</ref>，但在当天深夜又有回升。环流东南象限内发展出模糊的[[雨带|雨带]]，[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]测得的数值有所提高，气旋的卫星图像也变得更加清晰，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此于5月30日将位于[[埃斯孔迪多港_(瓦哈卡州)|埃斯孔迪多港]]以南约185公里海域的热带低气压升级成热带风暴并以“芭芭拉”（{{lang|en|Barbara}}）命名。[[2007年太平洋飓风季|2007年太平洋飓风季]]由此成为有纪录以来第3个在5月就有两场风暴形成的太平洋飓风季，之前两次分别是[[1956年太平洋飓风季|1956]]和[[1984年太平洋飓风季|1984年太平洋飓风季]]。气象部门起初预计芭芭拉会成为飓风，风速达到每小时135公里。<ref name="disc4">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-01 | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>

受[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]内上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]产向的北向气流影响，风暴向南飘移，之后又转向东进。由于[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]层次分明，行进洋面[[海面温度|水温]]较高，风暴的结构逐渐改善，中心附近发展出紧密的弧形雨带。<ref name="disc5">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Five | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.005.shtml | date =  }}</ref>但由于风切变增多，环流结构消退，到5月31日时风暴已开始减弱<ref name="disc8">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-01 | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.008.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。到了这天夜间，系统的大范围低压槽内已经形成非常紧密的小股环流<ref name="disc9">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.009.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170159/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.009.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>，气旋于6月1日清晨降级成热带低气压<ref name="disc10">{{cite report | author = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2007-05-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002123434/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.010.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.010.shtml | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。1号下午，系统再度发展出对流带，{{lang|en|[[QuikSCAT|QuikSCAT]]}}（意为“快速散射仪”）卫星数据表明气旋内已有层次分明的对流，芭芭拉因此再度升级成热带风暴<ref name="disc11">{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2007-05-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.011.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174257/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。风暴达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度，并因延伸至[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]西南部的[[高压脊|高压脊]]存在薄弱环节而转向东北<ref name="disc14">{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Fourteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175914/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.014.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.014.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。带状特征继续组织，并发展出下层[[风眼|眼状特征]]<ref name="disc15">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Fifteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185502/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.015.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.015.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}6月2日下午13点左右，气旋从墨西哥和[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]边境以西不远处[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。芭芭拉的中心在[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]最东南角的山脉上空迅速退化，很快就减弱成热带低气压，并且上岸仅12小时后就完全消散<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:TS_Barbara_(2007).jpg|right]]
气旋存在早期，美国国家飓风中心建议墨西哥西南沿海利益相关人员密切关注风暴动向<ref name="fa2">{{Cite report | author = Knabb | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Public Advisory Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.fstadv.002.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193728/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.fstadv.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。6月1日芭芭拉达到热带风暴强度后，危地马拉和墨西哥政府发布向危地马拉[[埃斯昆特拉省|埃斯昆特拉省]]度假小镇[[锡帕卡特|锡帕卡特]]（{{lang|en|Sipacate}}）到墨西哥巴拉托纳拉（{{lang|en|Barra de Tonala}}）之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref name="pa12">{{cite report |author1=Brown |author2=Avila |year=2007 |title=Tropical Storm Barbara Public Advisory Twelve |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.public.012.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.public.012.shtml? |accessdate=2016-01-20 |archivedate=2016-01-20 |deadurl=no |date= }}</ref>。随着气旋移动方向渐趋明朗，之前发布的热带风暴观察预警升级成热带风暴警告<ref name="pa13">{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Public Advisory Thirteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234352/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.public.013.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.public.013.shtml? | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>，且热带风暴观察预警的生效范围还向西延伸至墨西哥瓦哈卡州的[[萨利纳克鲁斯|萨利纳克鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Salina Cruz}}）<ref name="pa14">{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Public Advisory Fourteen | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220109/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.public.014.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.public.014.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。墨西哥政府向恰帕斯州和瓦哈卡州南部地区拨款，准备应对洪灾所需物资<ref name="ap62">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142237/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-barbara-gains-momentum/ | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-barbara-gains-momentum/ | work = CBS News | date = 2007-06-02 | deadurl = no | author = Associated Press | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Gains Momentum | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-01-20 }}</ref>。恰帕斯州至少有1400人撤离到避难所<ref name="ap63">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barry weakens to tropical depression, brings needed rain across Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071007231134/http://www.pr-inside.com/tropical-storm-barry-weakens-to-tropical-r142228.htm | accessdate = 2007-06-02 | url = http://www.pr-inside.com/tropical-storm-barry-weakens-to-tropical-r142228.htm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2007-10-07 }}</ref>。

气旋的外围雨带从6月1日晚开始影响危地马拉和墨西哥东南部<ref name="pa13" />。恰帕斯州的维斯特拉（{{lang|en|Huixtla}}）测得的24小时降雨总量最高，达到126毫米<ref name="smn">{{cite web | author = Alberto Hernández Unzón & Cirilo Bravo Lujano | year = 2007 | title = Reseña de la Tormenta Tropical "Barbara" del Océano Pacífico | publisher = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional | accessdate = 2007-07-10 | archivedate = 2007-09-28 | deadurl = yes | url = http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2007/pacifico/barbara/barbara.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928020451/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2007/pacifico/barbara/barbara.pdf }}</ref>，降水令墨西哥东南部各地的许多河流超过正常水位<ref name="reuters62">{{cite news | author = Mica Rosenberg | title = Tropical storm lashes Guatemala, Mexico coasts | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120142237/http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN02390123._CH_.242020070602 | url = http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN02390123._CH_.242020070602 | date = 2007-06-02 | archivedate = 2016-01-20 }}</ref>。系统登陆后不久，位于墨西哥马德罗港（{{lang|en|Puerto Madero}}）的地面自动气象站测得的持续风速为每小时58公里，阵风时速85公里<ref name="disc16">{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Avila | year = 2007 | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Sixteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190050/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/ep02/ep022007.discus.016.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。大部分地区因这场风暴引发的破坏程度很轻，仅限于灯柱倒塌、屋顶受损和短时停电<ref name="afp62">{{Cite web | author = Agence France-Presse | year = 2007 | title = Pasa tormenta tropical "Bárbara" por Chiapas | accessdate = 2007-09-26 | url = http://www.diario.com.mx/nota.php?notaid=fa7f902099d5a36b83ac168629b96bf3 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070926220343/http://www.diario.com.mx/nota.php?notaid=fa7f902099d5a36b83ac168629b96bf3 | archivedate = 2007-09-26 }}</ref>。不过，恰帕斯州南部山脉地区因气旋产生的狂风暴雨受到中到重度农作物损失。约有90平方公里香蕉作物毁于一旦，10平方公里咖啡作物受损。芭芭拉还对沿途的可可豆、芒果、椰子和蔬菜构成重创，农作物损失总额约有2亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（2007年墨西哥比索，相当于同年的5500万美元），墨西哥政府为此向受灾农民提供总额约1.08亿墨西哥比索（2007年墨西哥比索，相当于同年的2970万美元）。<ref>{{cite web | author = El Universal | year = 2007 | title = Destruye tormenta tropical más de 9 mil hectáreas de plátano | accessdate = 2007-07-26 | url = http://www.teorema.com.mx/articulos.php?id_sec=47&id_art=4064&id_ejemplar=0 | archivedate = 2007-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071106000706/http://www.teorema.com.mx/articulos.php?id_sec=47&id_art=4064&id_ejemplar=0 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

危拉马拉边境附近的[[奥科斯|奥科斯]]有约十幢棕榈木屋的屋顶被狂风摧毁<ref name="reuters62" />，上百位居民被迫疏散<ref name="ap63" />。沿海地区还有数以百计的树木被风刮倒。芭芭拉产生的强降雨导致河流泛滥，连接奥科斯岛和该国主大陆的桥梁被冲毁，两地交通中断。<ref name="reuters62" />风暴外围的暴雨在[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]引发严重洪灾，至少4人因此遇难<ref>{{cite news | agency = Saudi Press Agency | publisher = Saudi Press Agency | date = 2007-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150217123219/http://www.sauress.com/en/spaen/455075 | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | title = Heavy rain leaves 12 dead in Caribbean, Central America | url = http://www.sauress.com/en/spaen/455075 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-02-17 }}</ref>。

